6
00:01:27.921 --> 00:01:29.255
ako ay…

7
00:01:30.298 --> 00:01:31.466
ayos lang ako.

8
00:01:32.258 --> 00:01:33.218
okay lang ako.

9
00:01:39.766 --> 00:01:40.975
Mayroon akong malaking balita!

10
00:01:41.643 --> 00:01:44.979
Nang marinig ko ang bulung-bulungan
tungkol kay Propesor Seo at Dr. Cha,

11
