183
00:12:01.137 --> 00:12:03.472
Kung ayaw mo siyang makita,
hindi mo kailangan.

184
00:12:03.556 --> 00:12:05.558
Hindi, magkita tayo.

185
00:12:06.725 --> 00:12:08.269
I think magiging masaya kung magkikita tayo.

