199
00:13:20.090 --> 00:13:21.091
Syempre.

200
00:13:21.175 --> 00:13:24.345
Oo, ngunit dapat kang matakot
the fact that I-rang and I both

201
00:13:24.428 --> 00:13:25.971
ayoko pumasok sa med school.

202
00:13:29.600 --> 00:13:32.144
Well, medyo nadismaya ako.

203
00:13:33.354 --> 00:13:34.980
Pero paano kayo naging magkaibigan?

204
00:13:36.398 --> 00:13:38.901
Alam kong nasa iisang akademya kami,
kaya kusa akong lumapit sa kanya.

205
00:13:42.321 --> 00:13:43.155
Eun-seo!

206
00:13:45.616 --> 00:13:46.450
Bakit?

207
00:13:46.534 --> 00:13:47.535
