216
00:14:46.010 --> 00:14:48.012
Naisip ko lang na dapat mong malaman.

217
00:14:48.596 --> 00:14:52.808
Ang walang muwang mong pag iisip
inis talaga ako this entire time.

218
00:14:53.934 --> 00:14:55.185
Hindi mo ba gets?

